  "texts": [
    "To maximize their utility, it is essential to design Early Warning FMs with user-friendly interfaces that can be easily utilized by non-technical personnel.",
    "This would enable these systems to actively contribute to crisis meetings, offering realtime data analysis, predictive modeling, and actionable insights.",
    "The ability to simulate potential scenarios further enriches their contribution, offering foresight into possible outcomes and aiding in proactive decision-making.",
    "Future research should focus on the practical implementation of these models in real-world EWSs, including the development of robust evaluation metrics, and potentially benchmark tasks and simulations to assess their performance and impact.",
    "Overcoming challenges related to acquisition and management of high-quality training data will be critical to realize the potential of EWS FMs."
